{"id":148034,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/洛桑桑盖当选为西藏流亡政府新领导人/","date":"2011-04-27T07:00:27Z","modified":"2011-04-27T07:00:27Z","title":"洛桑桑盖当选为西藏流亡政府新领导人","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">达兰萨拉</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">据法新社报道，现年</span><span>43</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁的美国哈佛学者洛桑桑盖（</span><span>Obsang Sangay</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）成为西藏流亡政府下届领导人。根据流亡政府周三（</span><span>4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>27</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日）公布的选举结果，洛桑桑盖在上月的选举中获得</span><span>55%</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的选票，轻易击败另两名竞选人，当选为流亡政府下届首席部长。在达赖喇嘛宣布不再担任政治职务后，流亡政府新首脑的选举引起各方高度关注。作为新一代政治领导人，桑盖已明确表示，他完全支持达赖喇嘛提倡的</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中间道路</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15031948%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E6%B4%9B%E6%A1%91%E6%A1%91%E7%9B%96%E5%BD%93%E9%80%89%E4%B8%BA%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F%E6%B5%81%E4%BA%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%96%B0%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E4%BA%BA\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /